short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export all open tabs in the current window to a .txt text file.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
"Export Tabs" is a productivity-focused Chrome extension that enables users to export all open tabs in their current browser window into a convenient `.txt` file. 

Designed to streamline your browsing experience, "Export Tabs" is perfect for saving your browsing sessions, managing large numbers of tabs, and keeping track of important information. It's as simple as clicking the extension's icon - instantly, you'll have a text file with the URLs of all your open tabs.

Download "Export Tabs" today and revolutionize the way you manage your browsing sessions. This utility is a must-have for researchers, multitaskers, and anyone who values organization and time management. 

"Export Tabs" - keeping your browsing organized with just a click.
